{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_Overview.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Match Tree is a match 3 game, where each of your turns has consequences.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Merge plants sown by pixies, gnomes and witches.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bushes become trees, trees become houses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The rules are simple, the levels are short and you will refine your puzzle skills with each round.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you clever enough to face the challenges of the various levels?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_GnomePlants.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The characters sow plants for you to merge and upgrade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_Matches.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The hex fields allow a multitude of different combinations. Decide how many plants you merge and where to grow the result.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_MoveWitch.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s your decision where to place characters, when they are stuck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_Tools.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use tools, like the magic wand to solve tricky situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_Sheep.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But beware of the hangry sheep!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737661349","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737661349","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737661349","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737661349","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_Overview.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Match Tree is a match 3 game, where each of your turns has consequences.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Merge plants sown by pixies, gnomes and witches.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bushes become trees, trees become houses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The rules are simple, the levels are short and you will refine your puzzle skills with each round.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you clever enough to face the challenges of the various levels?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010870/extras/MatchTree_GnomePlants.gif?t=1737661349\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The characters sow plants for you to merge and upgrade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st